hatching larvae have to go through various stages of development before they become mature mosquitoes, and at each stage the young mosquitoes have different needs. Moreover, drought or severe heat can hinder the development of the eggs. For this reason, t
he mother mosquito has to find an environment in which the young she will produce can comfortably complete their development. }{\f0\fs22\insrsid3626024\charrsid15433267 
