e of all its effort. The laborious task it carries out has no effect on its own life. That is to say, the mosquito doesn\rquote 
t go to these lengths to stay alive, but to save the next generation. It makes the most appropriate decision and does all the necessary
 things to perfection to succeed in a difficult task to save a generation it will never see, and will never know what conditions it will develop under and what dangers it will face.}{\f0\fs22\expnd-1\expndtw-5\insrsid15433267\charrsid15433267  }{
