\par }{\f0\fs22\insrsid4280561 -}{\f0\fs22\insrsid3626024\charrsid15433267 Giving a local anaesthetic before an operation is a technique that has been developed with the help of medical knowledge. How has the mosquito acquired this knowledge? 
